Class SpectrumExperimentType<T extends SpectrumConfiguration>

    public abstract class SpectrumExperimentType<T extends SpectrumConfiguration>
extends Object
implements ExperimentType<T>
    Configure the sample position to perform an experiment at. Typically most other experiment nodes will be descendant to a sample experiment node, such that they operate on the configured sample.
